## Merge Lines

select the lines, which include `<li>`

```html
<ul>
  	<li class="list1"></li>
  	<li class="list2"></li>
  	<li class="list3"></li>
</ul>
```

and then type `<c-y>m`

```html
<ul>
  	<li class="list1"></li><li class="list2"></li><li class="list3"></li>
</ul>
```

